AI ethical approaches focus on ensuring that artificial intelligence is built and used in ways that are fair, safe, and accountable. With AI systems now deeply involved in decision-making, education, healthcare, and business, ethics has become a core part of the conversation. Institutions, companies, and governments are shaping frameworks to guide responsible AI development. For professionals aiming to gain credibility in this area, pursuing an AI certification is a practical first step. https://www.blockchain-council.org/certifications/certified-bitcoin-expert-cbie/
